title: Cheesy Chicken Rolls
ingredients: ['4 skinless, boneless chicken breast fillets, pounded to 5mm thickness', '115g Swiss cheese, such as Gruyere or Emmental, sliced', '115g thinly sliced ham', '2 tablespoons grated Parmesan cheese', '1 1/2 teaspoons paprika', '1/2 teaspoon garlic salt', '1/2 teaspoon dried tarragon', '1/2 teaspoon dried basil leaves', '1 tablespoon melted butter', '5 tablespoons dry breadcrumbs']
